  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a cast-iron skillet over medium heat.",
    "Brush both sides of the bread slices with olive oil.",
    "Place the bread in the skillet and sear until charred spots appear, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Spread wok-hee sauce on the inside of each toasted bread slice.",
    "Layer sun-dried tomato slices, raw greens, cucumber strips, and mozzarella on one slice.",
    "Top with the second slice of bread, pressed lightly.",
    "Continue cooking for 1 minute to warm the fillings and melt the cheese.",
    "Remove from heat, slice in half, and serve immediately."
